name: Dasnow
tagline: Javascript plugin that create a snow curtain
body:
Javascript plugin, create a snow curtain.


USAGE: just include dasnow.js in header section.

```html
<html>
<head>
  <script language="Javascript" src="dasnow.js"></script>
  ...
```
